                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">policeman, M</hi> 82.) I produce a certificate—(<hi rend="italic">read—William Potter convicted April</hi>, 1847, <hi rend="italic">confined twelve months</hi>)—I was pre<lb></lb>sent—the prisoner is the man.</p>
